---
title: Lemony Chicken Caesar Pasta Salad with Baby Lettuce, Parmesan & Croutons
description: Meet the latest culinary mash-up you didn’t know you needed. This quick, Caesar-inspired pasta salad features curly cavatappi, garlicky chicken, crisp lettuce, creamy Caesar dressing, and lemon juice for extra brightness. And let’s not forget the most important part: crunchy croutons and shredded Parmesan cheese to top it all off!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/675747137668eda5b41131f8-12f093e9.jpeg
